# evaltool — LLM proxy credentials.
#
# Copy this file to ".llmcredentials" and replace the placeholder below with the
# API token for the LLM proxy (the endpoint configured in LLM_BASE_URL).
#
# In the Docker deployment this file is bind-mounted read-only into the container
# at /run/secrets/llmcredentials (see docker-compose.yml), and the app reads the
# token from it (LLM_API_KEY_FILE). The real ".llmcredentials" is gitignored —
# never commit it. Comment (#) and blank lines are ignored; the first real line
# is used as the bearer token.

REPLACE_WITH_YOUR_LLM_PROXY_TOKEN
